    "Although FCN integrates feature maps from different layers by adding values for each channel (add), U-Net concatenates the outputs of feature maps obtained from the Encoder by adding them in parallel to the Decoder's feature maps (concatenate).",
    "Therefore, U-Net can learn while distinguishing between Encoder and Decoder feature maps.",
